      "content": "that makes sense. so when u say \"blend in seamlessly,\" u mean following the standard business protocols used in most major international hubs? like, if i'm in a place like london, new york, or singapore, what are the specific \"gold standards\" for things like dining etiquette or how to communicate to ensure i'm perceived as truly elite and high-status?",
